div.h3: VDBE Register Mapping: Multi-Table JOIN & Aggregation

p.code: SELECT users.name, SUM(orders.amount) FROM users JOIN orders ON users.id = orders.userid GROUP BY users.name

ul.li: R1-R4: Data slots extracted from B-tree cells via OP_Column.
R5: Special register holding a pointer to the AggContext (Milestone 11).
R6: Control-flow register determining if OP_Next should be skipped.
